body_html:
@guschmue
I guess there is a problem with the line 81 in tf_core_gpu_kernels_generated_adjust_contrast_op_gpu.cu.cc.obj.RelWithDebInfo.cmake
the line is
set(CUDA_NVCC_COMPILE_DEFINITIONS "EIGEN_AVOID_STL_ARRAY;NOMINMAX;_WIN32_WINNT=0x0A00;LANG_CXX11;COMPILER_MSVC;VERSION="MSVC";WIN32;OS_WIN;_MBCS;WIN64;WIN32_LEAN_AND_MEAN;NOGDI;PLATFORM_WINDOWS;TENSORFLOW_USE_EIGEN_THREADPOOL;EIGEN_HAS_C99_MATH;_ITERATOR_DEBUG_LEVEL=0;GOOGLE_CUDA=1;TF_EXTRA_CUDA_CAPABILITIES=3.5,5.2") # list (needs to be in quotes to handle spaces properly).

when I print the value of CUDA_NVCC_COMPILE_DEFINITIONS , I get the following:
EIGEN_AVOID_STL_ARRAY;NOMINMAX;_WIN32_WINNT=0x0A00;LANG_CXX11;COMPILER_MSVC;VERSION=;MSVC";WIN32;OS_WIN;_MBCS;WIN64;WIN32_LEAN_AND_MEAN;NOGDI;PLATFORM_WINDOWS;TENSORFLOW_USE_EIGEN_THREADPOOL;EIGEN_HAS_C99_MATH;_ITERATOR_DEBUG_LEVEL=0;GOOGLE_CUDA=1;TF_EXTRA_CUDA_CAPABILITIES=3.5,5.2"

there is an " after MVSC. I guess the stray character referred belongs to this line.
